             <h3 class="title">
              <a href="/news/1500-undocumented-immigrants-now-being-housed-at-dallas-convention-center">
               1,500 undocumented immigrant teens now being housed at Dallas convention center
              </a>
             </h3>
            </header>
            <p>
             There are now 1,500 unaccompanied minors staying at the Kay Bailey Hutchison Convention Center in Dallas after being apprehended at the southern border.
            </p>
            <time class="time" datetime="2021-03-21T19:57:06-05:00">
             5 hours ago
            </time>

               <a href="/news/1500-undocumented-immigrants-now-being-housed-at-dallas-convention-center">
                1,500 undocumented immigrant teens now being housed at Dallas convention center
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>

            <div class="info">
             <header class="info-header">
              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/sports/doncic-scores-37-mavericks-rout-trail-blazers-132-92">
                Doncic scores 37, Mavericks rout Trail Blazers 132-92
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              Luka Doncic scored 37 points in three quarters, leading the Dallas Mavericks to a 132-92 rout of the Portland Trail Blazers on Sunday night.
             </p>

               </a>

               <a href="/news/us-unemployment-claims-rise-to-770000-with-layoffs-still-high">
                US unemployment claims rise to 770,000 with layoffs still high
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              The four-week average of claims, which smooths out weekly variations, dropped to 746,000, the lowest since late November.

            <div class="info">
             <header class="info-header">
              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/news/house-oks-bills-offering-pathway-to-legal-status-to-dreamers-farm-workers-other-immigrants">
                House OKs bills offering pathway to legal status to Dreamers, farm workers, other immigrants
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              The House voted Thursday to unlatch a gateway to citizenship for young Dreamers and immigrants who have fled war or natural disasters abroad, giving Democrats a win in the years first vote on an issue that once again faces a steep uphill climb in Congress.
             </p>

            <div class="info">
             <header class="info-header">
              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/news/trackdown-help-find-lawrence-salazars-killers">
                Trackdown: Help find Lawrence Salazar's killers
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              In this weeks Trackdown, Dallas police have asked the public to help find the killers of 39-year-old Lawrence Salazar, who was trapped in his garage apartment by gunfire and shot to death.
             </p>
